---
title: Jalapeño Popper Stuffed Burgers with Creamy Ranch Mayo, Crispy Fried Onions & Potato Wedges
description: Like a jalapeño popper? Dig a burger? Our chefs created this inventive hybrid that encases the components of a popper in a juicy patty for a burst of extra flavor in every bite. Sauté fresh jalapeño, combine with creamy, melty cheeses and bold seasonings, and press that spicy, tangy filling into the center of each patty. After a quick pan-sear, you’ll tuck the patties into soft potato buns and top with creamy ranch mayo and crispy fried onions (the perfect finishing touches for the occasion). Add a side of golden brown potato wedges, and you are poppin!
